&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Cloud concepts&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Core Azure services&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Security, privacy, compliance, and trust&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Azure pricing and support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h5 id=&quot;the-az-900-exam-costs-9900-moneybag&quot;&gt;The AZ-900 exam costs $99.00 :moneybag:&lt;/h5&gt;

